#

Easy Lobster Risotto

35 min
$20
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

SeafoodGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

ItalianComfort Food

Description

Creamy risotto infused with succulent lobster and a hint of lemon.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • lobster meat: 1 cup
  • chicken or seafood broth: 4 cups
  • shallots: 1, finely chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • white wine: 1/2 cup (optional)
